const EyeIcon = () => (
  <svg
    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
    width="18"
    height="18"
    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
    fill="none"
    stroke="currentColor"
    strokeWidth="2"
    strokeLinecap="round"
    strokeLinejoin="round"
    className="eye-icon"
  >
    <path d="M2 12s3-7 10-7 10 7 10 7-3 7-10 7-10-7-10-7Z"></path>
    <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"></circle>
  </svg>
)

export default EyeIcon
